graph LR
    Feast[Feast Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    Feast -->|container platform| K8s[Kubernetes 1.11.3+]
    Feast -->|runtime| Python[Python 3.11]
    Feast -->|operator runtime| Go[Go 1.22+]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    Feast -.->|persistent store| PostgreSQL[PostgreSQL 9.6+]
    Feast -.->|online store| Redis[Redis 5.0+]
    Feast -.->|object storage| S3[S3-compatible Storage]

    %% OpenShift/RHOAI Integration
    Feast -->|external access| Routes[OpenShift Routes]
    Feast -->|notebook integration| Notebooks[Kubeflow Notebooks]
    Feast -.->|TLS certs| CertManager[cert-manager]
    Feast -->|metrics| Prometheus[Prometheus]
    Feast -.->|authentication| OAuth[OpenShift OAuth]

    %% Internal RHOAI Dependencies
    Routes -->|API| OpenShift[OpenShift 4.17+]
    Notebooks -->|CRD| Kubeflow[Kubeflow]

    %% Client Integrations
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -.->|UI management| Feast
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|feature access| Feast
    WorkbenchUser[Data Scientists] -->|creates FeatureStores| Feast
    MLModels[ML Models] -->|feature retrieval| Feast

    %% Persistence Options
    subgraph PersistenceOptions["Storage Backends"]
        SQLiteStore[(SQLite<br/>Default)]
        PostgreSQLStore[(PostgreSQL<br/>Optional)]
        RedisStore[(Redis<br/>Optional)]
        S3Store[(S3<br/>Optional)]
    end

    Feast -->|registry/online| SQLiteStore
    Feast -.->|registry/online| PostgreSQLStore
    Feast -.->|online| RedisStore
    Feast -.->|offline/registry| S3Store

    %% External Services
    Feast -.->|auth tokens| OIDC[OIDC Provider]
    Feast -.->|feature sync| Git[Git Repository]

